in "The Bonfire of the Vanities." ; Photo, COLOR, FLAMEOUT: Tom Hanks finds 
himself in jail in "The Bonfire of the Vanities." Director Brian De Palma has 
turned Tom Wolfe's rich source material into a total disaster. Reviewed by 
Sheila Benson. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
