</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
PEOPLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Transamerica Corp. has named three senior operating executives to new corporate 
positions as group vice presidents. 
</P>
<P>
David R. Carpenter, 51, has been named group vice president-life insurance and 
asset management. Richard H. Finn, 56, becomes group vice president-finance. 
Gerald A. Isom, 52, is group vice president-property/casualty insurance and 
real estate tax service. Carpenter and Finn are based in Los Angeles; Isom is 
based in Woodland Hills. 
</P>
</TEXT>
