<P>
SOUP KITCHEN SEEKS DONATIONS OF TOYS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Someone Cares soup kitchen in Costa Mesa is accepting toy donations for 
distribution to needy children during the holidays. 
</P>
<P>
"We have received plenty of donated food, but we don't have enough toys for the 
kids, said Art Rorden, a volunteer at the kitchen. "Their little eyes really 
